==English==
===Adjective===
'''[[out]] of [[touch]]'''
#{{idiom}} no longer maintaining [[contact]] or [[communications]]
#:''I had been '''out of touch''' with my old friend for a long time when she called.''
#{{idiom}} no longer [[conversant]] with facts; not [[aware]] or [[realistic]]
#:''Did his answer strike you as '''out of touch''' with reality?''

